{"tid":297961,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【年經】Sony 定HTC","createTime":"2017-06-26T01:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T11:47:09.000Z","uid":102587,"like":15,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b0010a14628695b17f63e8e94829c8860825a364","tid":297961,"uid":102587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:44:49.000Z","msg":"HTC代表 11<br />\n<br />\nSony代表XZP<br />\n<br />\n用過HTC Hero，Sensation <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHTC 自從 M8之後廢左武功，去到今年的HTC11 先有翻D料到，上期U ultra 都虧虧地，好似M10 優化差，開apps慢用 emmc，又有大陸mon咁，<br />\n<br />\n但HTC 11 就覺項配備都OK，就算Market唔夠三叔勁，但消費姐自己都會留意倒。<br />\n<br />\n屌，如果用翻一體式金屬就Per鳩fect，同埋比翻個3.5mm 插口我。<br />\n<br />\nSony XZP:<br />\n<br />\n曾幾何時，用過Z1 Compact 同Z3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，用落先覺佢個2000萬相機係有限制，唔係自動波就2000萬，但Sony 有D自家app幾好，好似 相機果D 背景散焦(早撚過Iphone)同 Movie Creator，係相影拍片都唔錯，同埋防水機一用就翻唔倒轉頭，都依家XZP，都想買。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申，用緊LG V20，早期1月壞左部z3，唔想簡HTC10就買左V20，10太廢了。"},{"pid":"8f027399e533fdae7c91f884bb195e3bee82cd13","tid":297961,"uid":37688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:47:59.000Z","msg":"htc"},{"pid":"c159fe4fe8ec86e951c5ff64e17f94b0e4ff80ca","tid":297961,"uid":3128,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:54:01.000Z","msg":"兩舊屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4ed911649571641daa34652de0af74827e6d9f","tid":297961,"uid":102587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:56:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩舊屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有咩高見?"},{"pid":"6b25f70c588cc244e78f59531370936c8622db6a","tid":297961,"uid":39628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T02:01:18.000Z","msg":"哩兩部我都有諗過<br />\n最尾買U11, overall都無咩差得過XZP<br />\n但XZP鏡銀真係幾靚"},{"pid":"cb1337f098f268e31da95868cfbbd4f332f1623e","tid":297961,"uid":102587,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T02:08:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哩兩部我都有諗過<br />\n最尾買U11, overall都無咩差得過XZP<br />\n但XZP鏡銀真係幾靚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢兩部我自己都好難簡，<br />\n<br />\nHTC 好大缺點係 冇3.5，但色真係靚，<br />\n<br />\nSony 我覺得唯一缺點係 4k Mon，4K會拉低S835既 performance"},{"pid":"acad421050e4b2b3bedb5db4ed7b12d03544c667","tid":297961,"uid":4241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T02:13:34.000Z","msg":"Htc"},{"pid":"491afc9307a42b9e303c14945293c7c6981a8723","tid":297961,"uid":39628,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T02:21:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>哩兩部我都有諗過<br />\n最尾買U11, overall都無咩差得過XZP<br />\n但XZP鏡銀真係幾靚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢兩部我自己都好難簡，<br />\n<br />\nHTC 好大缺點係 冇3.5，但色真係靚，<br />\n<br />\nSony 我覺得唯一缺點係 4k Mon，4K會拉低S835既 performance</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我用藍芽, 3.5有冇唔關我事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見speed test, Sony係最快喎<br />\nHTC就緊貼住U11<br />\n電量test, XZP可能因為4k Mon, U11係最好<br />\n我自己都覺得U11電量唔錯<br />\n<br />\n指紋解鎖, 我會鍾意XZP, 見到review都覺得佢個解鎖幾快幾爽<br />\n同埋XZP防水好過U11, 台仔好多人投訴U11個防水<br />\n<br />\nU11個edge sense應該會越來越多野玩, 我set做back, 睇forum,單手都可以搞掂<br />\n<br />\n利申: 之前用左M7 4年, HTC粉絲"},{"pid":"80bf2832886ee2cc509169921c63d5bddd2de80d","tid":297961,"uid":102587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T02:26:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>哩兩部我都有諗過<br />\n最尾買U11, overall都無咩差得過XZP<br />\n但XZP鏡銀真係幾靚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢兩部我自己都好難簡，<br />\n<br />\nHTC 好大缺點係 冇3.5，但色真係靚，<br />\n<br />\nSony 我覺得唯一缺點係 4k Mon，4K會拉低S835既 performance</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我用藍芽, 3.5有冇唔關我事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見speed test, Sony係最快喎<br />\nHTC就緊貼住U11<br />\n電量test, XZP可能因為4k Mon, U11係最好<br />\n我自己都覺得U11電量唔錯<br />\n<br />\n指紋解鎖, 我會鍾意XZP, 見到review都覺得佢個解鎖幾快幾爽<br />\n同埋XZP防水好過U11, 台仔好多人投訴U11個防水<br />\n<br />\nU11個edge sense應該會越來越多野玩, 我set做back, 睇forum,單手都可以搞掂<br />\n<br />\n利申: 之前用左M7 4年, HTC粉絲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nspeed test 係 開app果D 定網速??<br />\n<br />\n同埋sony D 機，個design 係好靚，一跌就真係898，唔知HTC 喇我，都唔好好似小米，或者我部LG 咁禁跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c5d7197373d3b7c05640bc345d2d24d7ebb9f37","tid":297961,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T02:40:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>哩兩部我都有諗過<br />\n最尾買U11, overall都無咩差得過XZP<br />\n但XZP鏡銀真係幾靚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢兩部我自己都好難簡，<br />\n<br />\nHTC 好大缺點係 冇3.5，但色真係靚，<br />\n<br />\nSony 我覺得唯一缺點係 4k Mon，4K會拉低S835既 performance</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我用藍芽, 3.5有冇唔關我事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見speed test, Sony係最快喎<br />\nHTC就緊貼住U11<br />\n電量test, XZP可能因為4k Mon, U11係最好<br />\n我自己都覺得U11電量唔錯<br />\n<br />\n指紋解鎖, 我會鍾意XZP, 見到review都覺得佢個解鎖幾快幾爽<br />\n同埋XZP防水好過U11, 台仔好多人投訴U11個防水<br />\n<br />\nU11個edge sense應該會越來越多野玩, 我set做back, 睇forum,單手都可以搞掂<br />\n<br />\n利申: 之前用左M7 4年, HTC粉絲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nspeed test 係 開app果D 定網速??<br />\n<br />\n同埋sony D 機，個design 係好靚，一跌就真係898，唔知HTC 喇我，都唔好好似小米，或者我部LG 咁禁跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1. 開apps<br />\n2. HTC而家係玻璃...我都怕跌...Sony未跌都甩漆"},{"pid":"4bec11e35f5c7fd77125b4234add607147b8e73f","tid":297961,"uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T02:40:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>哩兩部我都有諗過<br />\n最尾買U11, overall都無咩差得過XZP<br />\n但XZP鏡銀真係幾靚</blockquote><br />\n<br />